    <style>
        header
      {
    margin: 10px;
    width: auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
     }


    main
    {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    margin-left: 50px;
    margin-right: 50px;
    }

    div1
    {
    background-color: cornsilk;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;

    border-radius: 20px;
    }

    div{
    background-color: cornsilk;
    margin-top: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    padding: 10px;
    font-size: 25px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    }

    .steps
    {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 30px;
    }
button {
    height: 60px;

    padding: 1.3em 3em;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #000;
    background-color: #f6d278;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 45px;
    box-shadow: 0px 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;
    cursor: pointer;
    outline: none;
  }
  
  button:hover {
    background-color: #23c483;
    box-shadow: 0px 15px 20px rgba(46, 229, 157, 0.4);
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-7px);
  }
  button:active {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header id="header">
            <img src="/assets/logo.png" alt="Logo">
            <form action="/login" method="get">
                <button id="loginBtn">Login</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/userRegister" method="get">
                <button id="signupBtn">Sign Up</button>
            </form>
    </header>
    
    <main id="bodyMain">
        
        <div1 id="leftpart">
            <img src="/assets/covid gif.gif" alt="covid img1">
        <h2>ABOUT:</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to our webpage dedicated to COVID-19 vaccination in India. <br>
            The COVID-19 pandemic has impacted the world, and India has been one <br>
            of the countries significantly affected by the virus. As the second <br>
            most populous country in the world, India faced unique challenges in<br>
            managing the spread of the virus. However, through a robust vaccination<br>
            campaign and collective efforts, India is striving towards overcoming <br>
            this crisis and safeguarding its population.<br>
        </p>

        <h2>Vaccine Availability and Types:
        </h2>
        <p>
            India authorized several COVID-19 vaccines for emergency use, contributing <br>
            to a diverse portfolio of immunization options. These include <br>
            Covishield (developed by Oxford-AstraZeneca and manufactured by the Serum <br>
            Institute of India), Covaxin (developed by Bharat Biotech),<br>
            and Sputnik V (developed by Russia's Gamaleya Research Institute).<br>
            These vaccines have undergone rigorous testing and are proven to be safe<br>
            and effective in preventing severe illness and reducing transmission.<br>
        </p>

        </div1>

        <div id="rightpart">
            <h2 style="text-decoration:underline; color:darkgoldenrod; text-align: center;">
                Vaccination Steps:
            </h2>
            <p id="steps">
                1. Login/Signup with your details.         <br>
                2. Book Your Slot with the Nearest center. <br>
                3. Visit your Center on the booking day.   <br>
                4. Get your vaccination certificate.       <br>
            </p>
        </div>
        

    </main>
    
</body>
